title: nice collecable
review: this is my 6 time i am being first to review there is not much to review but there is two disks the color and the numbers are the only random part put the launcher is more powerful than the vahki's this was a nice 2003 set

author: legoguy2805
title: only 3 peices!
review: This set is really just a random Kanoka Disk launcher with two random Kanoka Disks. I got a Po-Metru Launcher with a Ta-Metru Disk and a Po-Metru Disk. A good set if you're in need of more ammo. Basically all there is to review.

author: Pepper
title: extra disk launcher ammo
review:
I got this set for my birthday in 2004 along with Tehutti and Ehrye. I also bought one on sale at 
K-Mart. Well onto the pros. and cons..

    Pros.
       disks
       thing that attaches disk launcher to the Bionicle
       disk launcher
       launches well

    Cons.
       don't know what disks you get

Overall buy only if you have a Bionicle.

author: Gus_263
title: Good Ammo Option
review: I rate it 4/5. Basically, it is from who need ammo. But it can come with repeated disks, that happens to me, coming with two onu metru disks, and a red launcher. Overall good reposition of ammo, for matorans, toa or vahki.

author: vezon8764
title: Nice Kanoka Pack
review:
The only downside is that it gave me 2 Onu-Metru disks and a brown launcher, considering that I don't own Ahkmou, so this is only an extra disk pack for me.
Pros:
2 disks
Launcher
Pieces to hold launcher to hand
Cons:
Only 2 disks
Totally random, so sometimes you get 3 of the same colored launcher.
Get it if you want extra disks and launchers, but it's not really worth 5 bucks or 3 bucks.

author: wadaltmon
title: More and More Ammo!
review: This set isn't an actual model, but it is great. I got about 3 of these, and I got a green launcher only- the others didn't come with a launcher! Faulty! But, then again, I got LOTS of disks and I hope you try to find one of these somewhere- an awesome one.

author: d_brick
title: discuses
review:
i am reviewing this set: kanoka disk pack

Pros

  • Pro 1: 2-3 disks every time
  • Pro 2: I got 2 lvl. 4+ disks

Cons

  • Con 1: flimsy launcher

so if you just want disks, and already have a launcher,then you should get this set.

author: Cligra
title: You get what you see...
review: Well, as the title says, you see what you get. This set contains a few of the highly collectable Kanoka Discs, and a launcher. Not the most thrilling set, but better then its equivalents in later years (such as set 8748). Not the most interesting set, but nice enough if you collect Kanoka.
